<p><strong>Scenario</strong></p>
</td>
<td width="189">
<p><strong>Structure</strong></p>
</td>
<td width="189">
<p><strong>Example</strong></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td width="189">
<p>Basic structure.</p>
</td>
<td width="189">
<p>[Intervention] for [health problem].</p>
</td>
<td width="189">
<p>Antibiotics for chronic periodontitis.</p>
