<div id="specialissue">
<h3>SPECIAL ISSUE</h3>
<p>Manuscripts for a thematic volume or issue. This manuscripts are requested by the editor in chief.</p>
<p><strong>Editors:</strong> Edison Andrés Cruz Olivo and Judy Elena Villavicencio</p>
<p>□ Open Submissions □ Indexed □ Peer Reviewed</p>
